ds.ov2.util
Class APDU_boolean

java.lang.Object
  ds.ov2.util.APDU_boolean
All Implemented Interfaces:
APDU_Serializable
public class APDU_boolean
extends Object
implements APDU_Serializable

APDU_Serializable wrapper around a boolean. The boolean is encoded as one byte, which is either 0 or 1, as every C programmer would expect.
